TEXT 56 592 Left 1 ;Notes:\nNodes JP1-8 can connect directly to BB pins TL1-16, BL1-16 (left hand BB)\nNodes JP9-16 can connect directly to BB pins TR2-17, BR1-16 (right hand BB)\nBB pin TL17 can connect to any of JP1-4 and JP13-16\nBB pin TR1 can connect to any of JP1-4 and JP13-16\nNodes JP1-4 can connect directly to any of JP9-12 (and JP5-8*)\nNodes JP13-16 can connect directly to any of JP5-8 (and JP9-12*)\nAINH, BINH, CINH, AWG1, AWG2 can connect directly to any of JP1-4 and JP13-16
